---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout title="Listen" description="Podcasts from Human on Purpose: Deep Fake Conversations and Bible 101.">

  <section class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6 pt-16 pb-20">

    <h1 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-heading font-medium mb-4">Listen</h1>
    <p class="text-text-secondary leading-relaxed mb-14">
      Two podcasts. Two very different formats. Both built to help you think more clearly
      about the things that matter most.
    </p>

    <!-- DFC -->
    <div class="mb-16">
      <div class="border-l-2 border-accent pl-6">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-heading font-medium mb-3">Deep Fake Conversations</h2>
        <p class="text-sm text-text-secondary uppercase tracking-wide mb-4">Weekly</p>
      </div>
      <div class="space-y-4 text-text-secondary leading-relaxed mt-4">
        <p>
          What would it sound like to sit down with C.S. Lewis? Or Aristotle? Or
          Viktor Frankl?
        </p>
        <p>
          Deep Fake Conversations uses AI-generated voices to bring history's most
          interesting thinkers back to the table for real conversations about the ideas
          that shaped the world.
        </p>
        <p>
          It's part history, part philosophy, part theater - and entirely honest about what it is.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="mt-6 flex flex-wrap gap-3">
        <a href="#" class="inline-block border border-border rounded-md px-4 py-2 text-sm text-text-secondary hover:border-accent hover:text-accent transition-colors">
          Apple Podcasts
        </a>
        <a href="#" class="inline-block border border-border rounded-md px-4 py-2 text-sm text-text-secondary hover:border-accent hover:text-accent transition-colors">
          Spotify
        </a>
        <a href="https://youtube.com/@HumanOnPurpose" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="inline-block border border-border rounded-md px-4 py-2 text-sm text-text-secondary hover:border-accent hover:text-accent transition-colors">
          YouTube
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Bible 101 -->
    <div>
      <div class="border-l-2 border-accent pl-6">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-heading font-medium mb-3">Bible 101</h2>
        <p class="text-sm text-text-secondary uppercase tracking-wide mb-4">Daily &middot; ~10 minutes</p>
      </div>
      <div class="space-y-4 text-text-secondary leading-relaxed mt-4">
        <p>
          The entire Bible in a year. One session a day, explained in plain language with
          historical context, literary structure, and theological meaning - without the
          seminary jargon.
        </p>
        <p>
          Whether you've read the Bible twenty times or never opened it, Bible 101 meets
          you where you are. This tells the full story of the Bible, the arc of our
          relationship with the divine, in a way that informs how we should live. Less
          dogma, more wisdom.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="mt-6 flex flex-wrap gap-3">
        <a href="https://bible101.humanonpurpose.co" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="inline-block bg-accent text-white rounded-md px-4 py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-accent-hover transition-colors">
          Open Bible 101
        </a>
        <a href="#" class="inline-block border border-border rounded-md px-4 py-2 text-sm text-text-secondary hover:border-accent hover:text-accent transition-colors">
          Apple Podcasts
        </a>
        <a href="#" class="inline-block border border-border rounded-md px-4 py-2 text-sm text-text-secondary hover:border-accent hover:text-accent transition-colors">
          Spotify
        </a>
        <a href="https://youtube.com/@HumanOnPurpose" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="inline-block border border-border rounded-md px-4 py-2 text-sm text-text-secondary hover:border-accent hover:text-accent transition-colors">
          YouTube
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>

  </section>

</BaseLayout>
